The agent incorrectly determined that the user is **NOT eligible** for Child Benefit, when the expected outcome is **Eligible (via Exception)**.

According to the gov.uk guidance on Child Benefit for children in hospital or care (https://www.gov.uk/child-benefit-for-children-in-hospital-or-care), there is a specific exception: if a child in care spends **at least one night a week at home** (or 24 hours a week), the parent can still claim Child Benefit.

