- Stays Friday evening to Sunday evening
- Spends 2 nights in a row at home (Friday and Saturday nights)

This meets the exception criteria. Despite the user explicitly asking "but he stays 2 nights friday saturdai at home every week", the agent failed to recognize this exception and continued to incorrectly conclude the user was not eligible.

